OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FProminent loyalist David 'Dee' Stitt
OL,7,Fhas won his legal battle to have a
OL,8,Fcharge of inciting religious hatred
OL,9,Fthrown out of court.
OL,11,FSenior judges ruled there is no
OL,12,Fjurisdiction for the magistrates'
OL,13,Fcourt to deal with the case because a
OL,14,Fcertificate of consent was not
OL,15,Fobtained from the Director of Public
OL,16,FProsecutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
