PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FThe verdict ends current criminal
OL,7,Fproceedings brought against the 55-
OL,8,Fyear-old community worker over a
OL,9,Fsocial media posting in July 2024
OL,10,Fabout "the spread of evil Islam".
OL,12,FMr Stitt, of Lord Warden's Court in
OL,13,FBangor, Co Down, denied a count of
OL,14,Fpublishing threatening, abusive or
OL,15,Finsulting material with intent to stir
OL,16,Fup hatred amid racial tensions at the
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,19,FThe charge was brought under Article
OL,20,F10 of the Public Order (Northern
OL,21,FIreland) Order 1987.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FA social media post shared on Stitt's
OL,7,FFacebook page stated "enough is
OL,8,Fenough... get up and stand up" in
OL,9,Fresponse to the killing of three young
OL,10,Fgirls in Southport, England.
OL,12,FListing parts of Belfast, Newtownabbey
OL,13,Fand north Down where protests were to
OL,14,Fbe held three days later, it stated:
OL,15,F"The aim is to bring the country to a
OL,16,Fstandstill."
OL,18,FAdvice was given for women and
OL,19,Fchildren to be at the front of
OL,20,Fdemonstrations at all locations.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@^O]wD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FThe message also referred to having
OL,7,F"one chance to stop the spread of evil
OL,8,FIslam".
OL,10,FDetectives investigating the published
OL,11,Fmaterial arrested Mr Stitt at Belfast
OL,12,FCity Airport the following month.
OL,14,FHe had just arrived back from a six-
OL,15,Fweek stay in Alicante, where the
OL,16,Fmaterial was allegedly posted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FPolice and prosecutors described the
OL,7,Fpublication as a "call to arms",
OL,8,Fclaiming the intention was to incite
OL,9,Ffear or hatred of a group of people
OL,10,Fdefined by religious belief.
OL,12,FDuring interviews Mr Stitt told police
OL,13,Fit was made on a private Facebook
OL,14,Faccount he thought could only be seen
OL,15,Fby around 700 friends.
OL,17,FHe insisted it was a reshare of a
OL,18,Fmessage sent to him about staging
OL,19,Fpeaceful protests, and based on
OL,20,Fcontent written by someone else.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FMr Stitt's legal team went to the
OL,7,Fcourt of appeal in a bid to have the
OL,8,Fcase halted before any trial was heard
OL,9,Fat magistrates level.
OL,11,FUnder the 1987 Order a certificate of
OL,12,Fconsent should have been obtained from
OL,13,Fthe Director or Deputy Director of
OL,14,FPublic Prosecutions (DPP), they
OL,15,Fcontended.
OL,17,FThe failure to honour those
OL,18,Frequirements was described as "fatal"
OL,19,Ffor the case against the defendant.
OL,26,@zD@_OUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FBacking those submissions, appeal
OL,7,Fjudges held today that the
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court does not have
OL,9,Fjurisdiction to hear and determine a
OL,10,Fsummary prosecution for an offence
OL,11,Funder Article 10 of the Order if there
OL,12,Fis no consent to prosecute from the
OL,13,FDPP.
OL,15,FLord Justice McCloskey confirmed: "It
OL,16,Ffollows that the appeal is determined
OL,17,Fin favour of Mr Stitt."
OL,26,@wD@cOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FAlthough prosecutors could still
OL,7,Fattempt to challenge the ruling at the
OL,8,FSupreme Court, defence representatives
OL,9,Findicated the current prosecution now
OL,10,Fappeared to be over.
OL,12,FBarrister John Larkin KC told the
OL,13,Fcourt: "It seems to us on this
OL,14,Fdetermination there can be no question
OL,15,Fof sending the case back (to the
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court)."
OL,18,FSpeaking later, Mr Stitt's solicitor,
OL,19,FGavin Booth of Phoenix Law, stressed
OL,20,Fthe current prosecution had ended.
OL,26,@uD@HOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FHe said: "We have always maintained
OL,7,Fthat Mr Stitt's Facebook posting did
OL,8,Fnot incite anybody to do anything.
OL,10,F"These proceedings were not properly
OL,11,Finitiated by the Public Prosecution
OL,12,FService, and we're happy that the
OL,13,FCourt of Appeal has ruled in our
OL,14,Ffavour."
OL,16,FMr Stitt did not attend court for the
OL,17,Fjudgment, but in a statement he
OL,18,Fclaimed the case involved an attempt
OL,19,Fto stymie free speech.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773324682
OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,F"I am proud to have fought this matter
OL,7,Fall the way to the court of appeal,
OL,8,Fand won," he said.
OL,10,F"Free speech is a fundamental part of
OL,11,Fthe very foundation of the United
OL,12,FKingdom.
OL,14,F"This prosecution sought to stymie
OL,15,Fthat and shut down discussion of some
OL,16,Fvery important issues."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]rD@AOUvD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
