OL,3,CDee Stitt 'spread of evil Islam'
OL,4,Csocial media post case thrown out
OL,6,FThe statement added: "I look forward
OL,7,Fto celebrating with my family and
OL,8,Fgetting on with my life after this
OL,9,Funjust, and ultimately failed,
OL,10,Fpersecution."
